{"tid":1535931,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"作為今晚有份快閃既 我有啲野想講","createTime":"2019-09-03T13:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T02:07:27.000Z","uid":288121,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e46fad54ea731b9980b67af22d020c8b57347abe","tid":1535931,"uid":288121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:57:02.000Z","msg":"如果你係新上黎既full gear 和理非 <br />\n我拜託你唔好帶隊快閃 同埋行軍速度要快 <br />\n<br />\n首先一開始就唔應該旺角落行過去 <br />\n就算太子出口有狗又點？ <br />\n出口隔離已經狗屋啦<br />\n<br />\n之後去到狗屋 唔應該係隔離再傾點<br />\n行軍最重要就係時間<br />\nhit and run 講左幾多次<br />\n而今次之後一上前hit就要開遮陣上<br />\n因為啲狗狗真係好撚驚<br />\n頭先一上前準備hit就即刻開槍傷左手足<br />\n呢個call的確唔係完美<br />\n<br />\n呢篇可以一睇<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我正式宣布 再圍狗屋係傻仔\nhttps://lih.kg/1476517</code></pre><br />\n交通方法人夠其實可以直接跳黨鐵<br />\n只要啲狗唔知我地目的地係邊 佢地就好難封站捉人 所以鐵路係最快最好既交通<br />\n而因為要目的地保密 所以唔好落車先再聚人傾 最好自己一team傾完帶大隊 大家自己決定跟唔跟 <br />\n<br />\n係我打緊篇文果時已經有手足因為搭巴士被人捉 大佬呀有記者影住你仲搭咁耐唔落車 如果要搭巴士撤退唔該搭一兩個站就落車化整為零 因為而家任何交通工具都唔安全<br />\n<br />\n我係度為我頭先語氣重左屌手足而致歉<br />\n但我係度重申一次如果你係未準備好衝既full gear 和理非 <br />\n我絕對唔建議你參與快閃 進退要自己用腦用眼決定 唔係有人叫跑就跑 頭先一開完槍就成班跑到唔見影 唔該要退要望住一齊慢慢退<br />\n<br />\n另外建議大家真係想快閃狗屋 唔該準備定投擲物hit and run <br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"91948b85081994d1803793fe1cf13a1c33b7df6e","tid":1535931,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:57:34.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93da22b70292a62a29199b2b9ba571f8a39e5895","tid":1535931,"uid":79178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"作為參與過幾次快閃嘅人<br />\n想講散水應該要分開散<br />\n小心一獲熟<br />\n今晚要引以為戒<br />\n多謝手足"},{"pid":"a5c23ff3949c7ad6eff0b72d9ebdc097245cd425","tid":1535931,"uid":109866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b93c0469da48bd78dc4fa7c809aa02c74efa545","tid":1535931,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4230ed92a2e2dafe8a3b3f3a317a2e03b84af1b","tid":1535931,"uid":256131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:01:59.000Z","msg":"p牌無得推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cb66fed060f1fcc2a9e094b404239fee88b5b2","tid":1535931,"uid":267466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cHT9MRF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/th